<l>eṉaittoṉ ṟiṉitēkāṇ kāmamtām vīḻvār </l>
<l> niṉaippa varuvatoṉ ṟil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even to think of one's beloved gives one no pain. Sexuality, in any degree, is always delightful.</l>
